fields.content: Set competitive pricing: Make sure your pricing is competitive with other Airbnb listings in your area. Use the Airbnb pricing tool to help you set the right price for your listing.
Make sure to take clear, well-lit photos that showcase your property's best features.
Offer additional amenities: Consider offering additional amenities that can help your listing stand out, such as free Wi-Fi, a pool, or a hot tub.
